data.description: An incredibly rare opportunity to own this ADORABLE craftsman style home in the Heart of Leavenworth. Conveniently located within walking distance to restaurants, shopping, the community pool, schools, parks, and more! This adorable home features custom built-ins throughout, ample natural lighting, timeless finishes, and plenty of room to add a garage in the back. Vaulted ceilings expand your living space while enjoying the coziness of this floorplan. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house a home.
